{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be lively and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Vivid Games</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            background-color: #f0f0f0;\n            color: #333;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #d32f2f;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        header::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: -50%;\n            width: 150%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 10%, transparent 10%, transparent 90%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 90%);\n            animation: shimmer 2s infinite;\n        }\n        @keyframes shimmer {\n            0% { transform: translateX(0); }\n            100% { transform: translateX(30%); }\n        }\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #ffebee;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #d32f2f;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero-content {\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .hero-overlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: repeating-linear-gradient(\n                45deg,\n                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05),\n                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 10px,\n                transparent 10px,\n                transparent 20px\n            );\n            pointer-events: none;\n        }\n        .games {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #fff;\n        }\n        .games h3 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n        }\n        .game-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .game-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-bottom: 4px solid #d32f2f;\n        }\n        .game-card-content